(2306,'2','OPTIONAL','b','Does the written agreement contain transfer limits?-Contiene el acuerdo escrito límites de transferencias?','{"S8P6B":{"Id":"S8P6B","text":"","code":"crimes8p6b"}}','2304',''),
(2307,'2','OPTIONAL','c','Is verification, by someone other than the initiator of the transfer instruction, required prior to such transfer taking place?-Se requiere verificación por parte de una persona distinta al iniciante de la instrucción , previo a la ejecución de la transferencia?','{"S8P6C":{"Id":"S8P6c","text":"","code":"crimes8p6c"}}','2304',''),

(2308,'2','OPTIONAL','7','Are passwords used to give varying levels of access to your computer system and fund transfer system on the need and authorisation of user basis?-Son utilizadas claves para los distintos  niveles de acceso a un sistema de informatica y sistema de traspaso de fondos, dependiendo en la necesidad y autorización del usario?','{"S8P7":{"Id":"S8P7","text":"","code":"crimes8p7"}}','2290',''),

(2309,'2','OPTIONAL','8','Are all key source documents maintained in a secure environment prior to being entered into the computer system in order to prevent unauthorised modification or inappropriate use of data?-Son mantenidos todos los documentos claves en una ubicación segura previo a ser incluidos en la sistema de computación, de forma de prevenir la modificación  sin autorización o uso inapropiado de datos?','{"S8P8":{"Id":"S8P8","text":"","code":"crimes8p8"}}','2290',''),

(2310,'2','OPTIONAL','9','Are remote terminals kept in a physically secure location accessible by authorised personnel only?-Son los terminales remotos mantenidos en un ambiente físicamente seguro, con acceso restringido a personal autorizado únicamente?','{"S8P9":{"Id":"S8P9","text":"","code":"crimes8p9"}}','2290',''),

(2311,'2','OPTIONAL','10','Do you utilise any recognised software packages to control access to your computer system?-Utiliza paquetes de software reconocidos que controlan el acceso a su sistema informatico?','{"S8P10":{"Id":"S8P10","text":"","code":"crimes8p10"}}','2290',''),

(2312,'2','OPTIONAL','11','Are your data processing centres physically separated from other departments?-Estan sus centros de procesamiento de datos separados físicamente de los otros departamentos?','{"S8P11":{"Id":"S8P11","text":"","code":"crimes8p11"}}','2290',''),

(2313,'2','OPTIONAL','12','Do you have access control system for your data processing centres?-Tiene un sistema de control de acceso a su centro de procesamiento de datos?','{"S8P12":{"Id":"S8P12","text":"","code":"crimes8p12"}}','2290',''),

(2314,'2','OPTIONAL','13','Are data file generations stored and secured off-site in a restricted area?-Son las informaciones emanadas de archivos de datos guardadas y aseguradas en zonas restringidas?','{"S8P13":{"Id":"S8P13","text":"","code":"crimes8p13"}}','2290',''),

(2315,'2','OPTIONAL','14','Do you utilise independent contractors to prepare electronic computer programmes? If "yes"- Utiliza contratistas independientes para preparar programas informáticos?  En caso afirmativo:','{"S8P14":{"Id":"S8P14","text":"","code":"crimes8p14"}}','2290',''),
(2316,'2','OPTIONAL','a','Are specific parameters in place to restrict their access?-Existen parámetros específicos para restringir su acceso?','{"S8P14A":{"Id":"S8P14A","text":"","code":"crimes8p14a"}}','2315',''),
(2317,'2','OPTIONAL','b','Are their activities overseen when accessing your computer system?-Son supervisadas sus actividades cuando accedan a su sistema informatico?','{"S8P14B":{"Id":"S8P14B","text":"","code":"crimes8p14b"}}','2315',''),
(2318,'2','OPTIONAL','c','Are safeguards in place to prevent access to your other systems?-Existen medidas de seguridad para impedir el acceso a sus demás sistemas?','{"S8P14C":{"Id":"S8P14C","text":"","code":"crimes8p14c"}}','2315',''),

(2319,'2','DES','FUND/INVESTMENT/ASSET MANAGEMENT COMPANIES / FONDOS / COMPAÑIAS DE INVERSION Y MANEJO DE FONDOS','','','',''),
(2320,'2','DES','Only complete if the Proposer offers such services to third parties / Solo llenar en caso de que el Proponente ofrezca dichos servicios a Terceras Personas','','','2319',''),

(2321,'2','OPTIONAL','','1.Are transactions only entered into on the basis of appropriate authorisation in accordance with management criteria?-Son las transacciones únicamente ejecutadas con la apropiada autorización de acuerdo con los criterios de la dirección?','{"S9P1":{"Id":"S9P1","text":"","code":"crimes9p1"}}','2319',''),

(2322,'2','OPTIONAL','','2.Has management defined and communicated  formal trading policies and dealing limits?-Ha definido y comunicado la gerencia/directiva póliticas formales de transacciones así como limites transaccionales?','{"S9P2":{"Id":"S9P2","text":"","code":"crimes9p2"}}','2319',''),

(2323,'2','OPTIONAL','','3.Are trading transactions and positions reviewed for compliance with formal trading 	policies manual or similar internal document?-Son revisadas las transacciones y posiciones para evaluar su conformidad con manuales de póliticas transaccionales o algún documento interno similar?','{"S9P3":{"Id":"S9P3","text":"","code":"crimes9p3"}}','2319',''),

(2324,'2','OPTIONAL','','4.Are accounts of trades which exceed set limits identified or rectified or referred to senior management for immediate action?-Son las transacciones que exceden de límites establecidos identificados, rectificados o referidos a niveles superiores de gerencia para que acciones inmediatas sean tomadas?','{"S9P4":{"Id":"S9P4","text":"","code":"crimes9p4"}}','2319',''),

(2325,'2','OPTIONAL','','5.Do Counter parties receive authorised confirmation for all deals prior to settlement?-Recíben las contra-partes confirmación autorizada de toda negociación previas al pago de la mísma?','{"S9P5":{"Id":"S9P5","text":"","code":"crimes9p5"}}','2319',''),

(2326,'2','OPTIONAL','','6.Is the book of investments and securities periodically substantiated and evaluated against recorded values independently of the dealer and fund managers?-Es la cartera de inversiones periodicamente revisada y evaluada contra valores históricos , independientemente del negociador y gerente del fondo?','{"S9P6":{"Id":"S9P6","text":"","code":"crimes9p6"}}','2319',''),

(2327,'2','OPTIONAL','','7.Are responsibilities for investment decisions segregated from accounting activities and custodial responsibities?-Estan las responsabilidades de las decisiones de inversión separadas de las actividades contables así como de las responsabilidades de custodia?','{"S9P7":{"Id":"S9P7","text":"","code":"crimes9p7"}}','2319','');

